data.description: Motivated Seller will entertain all offers! Welcome home to this pretty much new home in Hacienda. Sellers are relocating and sad to leave their home that is still under 1 year builder warranty. Great sized living room and farmhouse ceiling fan that opens to the dining room which fits a dining room table with 6 chairs and sits between the living room and kitchen. Plenty of counterspace in this kitchen with grey cabinets and electric stove and dishwasher. Breakfast nook with a light fixture installed adding a nice touch. Sliding doors take you outside to your patio that is perfect for BBQing. Primary bedroom is spacious allowing oversized furniture. Primary bathroom with a stand up shower and double vanity and walk in closet. Secondary bedrooms are split from primary offering privacy. Guest room and 2nd room share the hall bath that provides a bathtub shower combo. 2 car garage. Walking distance to the community park area. Easy access to Hwy and shopping.
